This script manage PP docking work flow.

tools
        1. Ftdock 
        2. Zdock 
        3. Rosetta 
        4. Gramm-X http://vakser.bioinformatics.ku.edu/resources/gramm/grammx (in plans)
	5. CABS (in plans)

To run the script:
dodock.pl opcje molstatic molmobile


